Package: simplystats
Title: Make simplystats themed plots
Version: 0.1
Author: Jeffrey T. Leek <jtleek@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows people to make plots using the simplystats
    theme. For now these plots are in base R graphics, because we are old
    foggies, but eventually we might get around to making a ggplot2 theme (or
    someone could send us a pull request).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1),
    grid,
    png,
    RColorBrewer
Maintainer: Jeffrey T. Leek <jtleek@gmail.com>
License: MIT
LazyData: true
